  <scopecontent id="aspace_f8b984c7ac8e1348498bb2a4229863b4">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Historical material relating to the Chemistry Department includes photographs (including prints, and glass and film slides), articles, lecture notes, memorabilia, correspondence, tape recordings, programs, material on professorial exchanges, and announcements; also, photographs documenting the construction of Baker Laboratory; and a history of the department by Emile Chamot and Fred H. Rhodes.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <odd id="aspace_63d75d1e5789983aaacbfc46d7bc4f9d">
